{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Corellian_Harvest_Festival",
  "title": "The Corellian Harvest Festival",
  "summary": "Lord Smitherbodkins opens his Galactic Swoop League parade and Corellian Harvest Festival in Imperial-held Coronet City, drawing a sprawling crowd that includes disguised New Republic operatives, Imperial officers, and assorted onlookers. When a censored New Republic float rolls past, alien activists storm it shouting 'Free Corellia!' and shower the crowd with anti-Imperial propaganda, triggering brawls, Imperial crackdowns, and chaos that overruns the event. Admiral Danik Kreldin confronts Smitherbodkins over the rebel float while the smuggler Lando Calrissian, spotted in the throng, slips his Imperial captors and escapes with Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard and her escort, aided by sleight of hand and the cover of the panicking crowd. The Espo Mirhoz is stunned trying to take Lando into custody, the Sullustan agent Enb'Zik and his colleague Paris nearly blow their covers, and General Morrison Van Sen locks down the city's spaceport to prevent Lando's flight. As the final harvest float limps past and the crowd disperses under threat of gas, Danik orders a planet-wide manhunt and bounty on Calrissian, who quietly diverts to a safehouse rather than risk the watched starport.",
